{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4e05c334d5","title":"读《古文辞类集》批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"5cca959b33","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指“临乱之君，各贤其臣”一语。"},{"id":"2ca44e6a3a","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指战国时秦将白起、王剪，赵将廉颜、李牧。"}],"contents":[{"id":"806c2e9cbd","type":"title","text":"读《古文辞类集》批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5cca959b33","type":"subtitle","text":"读《古文辞类集》批语","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"2ca44e6a3a","type":"paragraph","text":"后汉献帝时，尽取天下名士因禁之，目为党","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"9bca0ca431","type":"paragraph","text":"在献帝以前","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"60b6189759","type":"paragraph","text":"人。及黄巾贼起，汉室大乱，后方悔悟，尽解党","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b3f3ba7ec3","type":"paragraph","text":"人而释之，然已无救奖。唐之晚年，渐起朋党之","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5e82a5e38f","type":"paragraph","text":"论，及昭宗时，尽杀朝之名士，咸投之黄河，","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"d50a700f05","type":"paragraph","text":"似是而非。日：此辈清流，可投浊流。而唐遂亡奖。夫前世汉献、唐昭时，之主，能使人人异心不为朋，莫如；能禁绝善政在权臣，非倪人为朋，莫如汉献帝；能课裂清流之朋，莫如唐偏皇帝之罪。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"de61520fe3","type":"paragraph","text":"昭宗之世：然皆乱亡其国。更相称美推让而不自","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5f05df983d","type":"paragraph","text":"疑，莫如算之二十二臣，舜亦不疑而皆用之。然","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"1f5ef67813","type":"paragraph","text":"而后世不请舜为二十二人朋党所欺，而称舜为聪","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b1fa22fcd0","type":"paragraph","text":"明之圣者，以能辨君子与小人也。周武之世，举","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"12b1411bfc","type":"paragraph","text":"其国之臣三千人共为一朋，自古为朋之多且大，","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5379aeb1ce","type":"paragraph","text":"莫如周。然周用此以兴者，善人虽多而不厌也。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"e36a805ba5","type":"paragraph","text":"夫兴亡治乱之迹，为人君者，可以鉴奖。[论辨","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"f0da8eb9ee","type":"paragraph","text":"类，欧阳永叔《朋党论》","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"a319d25b1b","type":"paragraph","text":"前世为人君者，力拒群议，专信一人，而不","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"16811543bf","type":"paragraph","text":"能早悟以及于福败者多奖，不可以遍举，请试举","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"585f40518b","type":"paragraph","text":"错在倾巢而其一二：普秦符坚地大兵强，有众九十六万，号出。若一二十万称百万，茂视东普，指为一偶，谓可直以气香之人更番送试，胜耳。然而举国之人，皆言晋不可代，更进互说者则进，败则止，不可胜数，其所陈天时人事，坚随以强辨折之，未必不可为。","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"687a4856b0","type":"paragraph","text":"忠言说论，皆泪屈而去。如王猛、荷融，老成之","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"fa3022bc07","type":"paragraph","text":"言也，不听；太子宏、少子洗，至亲之言也，不","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"4a3d548609","type":"paragraph","text":"听；沙门道安，坚平生所信重者也，数为之言，","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"65778e2f6f","type":"paragraph","text":"不听。惟听信一将军慕容垂者。垂之言日：“","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"abc3872d2f","type":"paragraph","text":"下内断神谋足奖，不烦广询朝臣以乱圣虑。坚","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"1b75e82fa5","type":"paragraph","text":"大喜日：“与吾共定天下者惟尔！”于是决意不","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"a732ec2d80","type":"paragraph","text":"疑，遂大举南伐。兵至寿春，普以数千人击之，","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"29ae0eea6d","type":"paragraph","text":"大败而归。北至洛阳，九十六万兵亡其八十六","index":26,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"ef051a6fa9","type":"paragraph","text":"万，坚自此兵威温丧，不复能振，遂至于乱亡。","index":27,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"46a19518a3","type":"paragraph","text":"近五代时，后唐清泰帝惠普祖之镇太原也，地近","index":28,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"8da3243f88","type":"paragraph","text":"契丹，特兵践息，议欲徒之于鄂州。举朝之士皆","index":29,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"230c03801f","type":"paragraph","text":"读以为未可，帝意必欲徒之。夜召常所与谋柜密","index":30,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"3e68a0f2c0","type":"paragraph","text":"直学士薛文遇，问之以决可否。文遇对日：“臣","index":31,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"2999cdbfd8","type":"paragraph","text":"闻作舍道边，三年不成，此事断在下，何必更","index":32,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"d7ad9ac97d","type":"paragraph","text":"问群臣？”帝大喜日：“术者言我今年当得一贤佐","index":33,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c0e848558f","type":"paragraph","text":"助我中兴，狮其是乎？”即时命学士草制，徒普","index":34,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b57ac340e6","type":"paragraph","text":"祖于郸州。明旦宣麻，在廷之臣皆失色。后六日","index":35,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"3c03cbee72","type":"paragraph","text":"而普祖反书至，清泰帝忧惧不知所为，谓李崧","index":36,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"d0e6aae3c4","type":"paragraph","text":"不徒石敬日：“我适见薛文遇，为之肉顿，欲自抽刀刺塘，没有薛文之。”崧对日：“事已至此，悔无及奖。”但君臣遇，照样亡国，相顾，沸泣而已。由是言之，能力拒群议专信一不过时间先后耳。人，莫如二君之果也，由之以致锅败乱亡，亦莫","index":37,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"aef46967f2","type":"paragraph","text":"如二君之酷也。方符坚欲与慕容垂共定天下，清","index":38,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"8431b7e4c9","type":"paragraph","text":"汉元帝语，泰帝以薛文遇为贤佐，助我中兴，可谓临乱之","index":39,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"47d199f784","type":"paragraph","text":"君，各贤其臣者也。或有话予日：然则用人者不也是一句空话。三可专信乎？应之日：齐恒公之用管仲，蜀先生之","index":40,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"4374138387","type":"paragraph","text":"用诸葛亮，可谓专而信奖，不闻举齐、蜀之臣民","index":41,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"22b1f39f5e","type":"paragraph","text":"非之也。盖其令出而举国之臣民从，事行而举国","index":42,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"e849f6cc44","type":"paragraph","text":"之臣民便，故恒公、先主得以专任而不贰也。使","index":43,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"bac0751ca2","type":"paragraph","text":"令出而两国之人不从，事行而两国之人不便，则","index":44,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"1b671e9837","type":"paragraph","text":"彼二君者，其肯专任而信之以失众心而敏国忽","index":45,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"96ab7190ae","type":"paragraph","text":"乎？[论辨类，欧阳永叔《为君难论》上]","index":46,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"2797ac36ca","type":"paragraph","text":"鸣呼！用人之难难奖，未若听言之难也。夫","index":47,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"42eaa17c3b","type":"paragraph","text":"人之言非一端也。巧辩纵横而可喜，忠言质朴而","index":48,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"6049ef80b2","type":"paragraph","text":"多钠，此非听言之难，在听者之明暗也；硬言顺","index":49,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"ba2d4b5d5a","type":"paragraph","text":"意而易悦，直言逆耳而触怒，此非听言之难，在","index":50,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5d5fb4e7e6","type":"paragraph","text":"听者之贤思也：是皆未足为难也。若听其言则可","index":51,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"153cfb17c0","type":"paragraph","text":"用，然用之有辆败人之事者；听其言若不可用，","index":52,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"bf93dd8f87","type":"paragraph","text":"然非如其言不能以成功者，此然后为听言之难","index":53,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c156a66ed7","type":"paragraph","text":"也。请试举其一二：战国时赵将有赵括者，善言","index":54,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"1011507208","type":"paragraph","text":"兵，自谓天下莫能当。其父奢，赵之名将，老于","index":55,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"8ce72b7864","type":"paragraph","text":"用兵者也，每与括言，亦不能届。然奢终不以括","index":56,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"2ef291c3c6","type":"paragraph","text":"为能也，以日：“赵若以括为将，必败赵事。其","index":57,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"6a202b0066","type":"paragraph","text":"后奢死，赵遂以括为将。其母自见赵王，亦言括","index":58,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b0e5c32ef4","type":"paragraph","text":"不可用。赵王不听，使括将而攻秦，括为秦军射","index":59,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"53b0885884","type":"paragraph","text":"死，赵兵大败，降秦者四十万人，坑于长平。盖","index":60,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"f426c7806e","type":"paragraph","text":"当时未有如括善言兵，亦未有如括大败者也。此","index":61,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"221d211936","type":"paragraph","text":"听其言可用，用之辆败人事者，赵括是也。秦始","index":62,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"6158b64b6f","type":"paragraph","text":"皇欲代荆，问其将季信：“用兵几何？”信方年少","index":63,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"462f6d4c31","type":"paragraph","text":"而勇，对日：“不过二十万足奖。始皇大喜。又","index":64,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"88fabbb170","type":"paragraph","text":"以问老将王剪，剪日：“非六十万不可。”始皇不","index":65,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"67d8cee5bb","type":"paragraph","text":"悦目：“将军老奖，何其快也？”因以信为可用，","index":66,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"50fd5d89c6","type":"paragraph","text":"即与兵二十万，使伐荆。王透谢病，退老于频","index":67,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"0aa83c92e6","type":"paragraph","text":"阳。已而信大为荆人所败，亡七都射而还。始皇","index":68,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c74e968832","type":"paragraph","text":"大断，自驾如频阳谢剪，因强起之。剪日：“必","index":69,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"0316de9cb0","type":"paragraph","text":"欲用臣，非六十万不可。于是华与六十万而","index":70,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"0a006ec16b","type":"paragraph","text":"往，遂以灭荆。夫初听其言若不可用，然非如其","index":71,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b3e2345c3c","type":"paragraph","text":"言不能以成功者，王剪是也。且听计于人者宜如","index":72,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"45a2f4b3aa","type":"paragraph","text":"何？听其言若可用，用之宜奖，辆败事；听其言","index":73,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"cf60a53312","type":"paragraph","text":"若不可用，舍之宜奖，然必如其说则成功：此所","index":74,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b114d53bbe","type":"paragraph","text":"看什么新以为难也。予又以谓秦赵二主，非徒失于听言，进。起、剪、亦由乐用新进，忽弃老成，此其所以败也。大抵颜、牧\"其始皆新进之士喜勇锐，老成之人多持重，此所以人主新进也。周瑜、之好立功名者，听勇锐之语则易合，闻持重之言诸葛、郭嘉、贾则难入也。若赵括者，则又有说为。予略考《史谢，非皆少年新记》所书，是时赵方道廉颜攻奏。颜，赵名将进乎？","index":75,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"fec77e47f6","type":"paragraph","text":"也。秦人是颜而知括虚言易与也，因行反间于赵","index":76,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"00838c9132","type":"paragraph","text":"日：“秦人所晨者赵括也，若赵以为将，则秦惧吴。赵王不悟反间也，遂起括为将以代颜。简相如力读以为不可，赵王不听，遂至于败。由是言之，括虚谈无实而不可用，其父知之，其母亦知之，赵之诸臣商相如等亦知之，外至敌国亦知之，独其主不悟尔。夫用人之失，天下之人皆知其不可，而独其主不知者，莫大之思也。前世之锅乱败亡由此者，不可胜数也。[论辨类，欧阳永叔《为君难论》下]","index":77,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"ee7287f61b","type":"paragraph","text":"成、康爱而民生不见先王之治，日入于乱，以至于秦，尽除前圣数千载之法。天下既攻秦而亡之，以归于汉。汉之为汉，更二十四君，东西再有天下，垂四百年，然大抵多用秦法，其改更秦事，亦多附已意，非放先王之法而有天下之志也。有天下之志者，文帝而已。然而天下之材不足，故仁闻虽美奖，而当世之法度亦不能放于三代。汉亡，而强者遂分天下之地。晋与隋虽能合天下于一，然而合之未久而已亡，其为不足议也。代障者唐，更十八君，垂三百年，而其法莫尽于太宗之为君也。袖己从读，仁心爱人，可谓有天下之志。以租席任民，以府卫任兵，以职事任官，以材能任职，以兴义任俗，以尊本任众，赋役有定制，兵农有定业，官无虚名，职无废事，人习于善行，离于末作，使之操于上者要而不烦，取于下者集而易供，民有农之实而兵之备","index":78,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"d3b0691b35","type":"paragraph","text":"存，有兵之名而农之利在，事之分有归，而禄之","index":79,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"d0385b4eea","type":"paragraph","text":"出不浮，材之品不遗，而治之体相承，其廉耻日","index":80,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"fe4adf9e2e","type":"paragraph","text":"以驾，其田野日以辟，以其法修则安且治，废则","index":81,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"4c41554396","type":"paragraph","text":"危且乱，可谓有天下之材。行之数岁，栗米之","index":82,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"ad0ae0e185","type":"paragraph","text":"赋，斗至数钱。居者有余蓄，行者有余资。人人","index":83,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"a27617d5d8","type":"paragraph","text":"自厚，几致刑措，可谓有治天下之效。夫有天下","index":84,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"921b005ada","type":"paragraph","text":"此文什么也之志，有天下之材，又有治天下之效，然而不得没有说","index":85,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"45b14a3e8b","type":"paragraph","text":"与先王并者，法度之行，拟之先王未备也：礼乐","index":86,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"daf6faa60a","type":"paragraph","text":"之具，田嗨之制，库序之教，拟之先王未备也。","index":87,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"054f69e5bf","type":"paragraph","text":"亲行阵之间，战必胜，攻必克，天下莫不以为","index":88,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"e0e8a016d4","type":"paragraph","text":"武，而非先王之所尚也。四夷万里，古所未及以","index":89,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"820b9a1eb7","type":"paragraph","text":"政者，莫不服从，天下莫不以为盛，而非先王之","index":90,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"d8ff6cd325","type":"paragraph","text":"所务也。太宗之为政于天下者，得失如此。由唐","index":91,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"174874e627","type":"paragraph","text":"虞之治，五百余年而有汤之治；由汤之治，五百","index":92,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"acdd7211cb","type":"paragraph","text":"余年而有文、武之治；由文、武之治，千有余年","index":93,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"96feffb7cf","type":"paragraph","text":"而始有太宗之为君，有天下之志，有天下之材，","index":94,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"32f52d3598","type":"paragraph","text":"又有治天下之效。然而又以其未备也，不得与先","index":95,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"0244aadfc2","type":"paragraph","text":"王并而称极治之时，是则人生于文武之前者，率","index":96,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"46c44616af","type":"paragraph","text":"五百余年而一遇治世；生于文武之后者，千有余","index":97,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b601fbc0c5","type":"paragraph","text":"年而未遇极治之时也。非独民之生于是时者之不","index":98,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"81cfb7ddab","type":"paragraph","text":"幸也。士之生于文武之前者，如舜、禹之于唐，","index":99,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"cc50585fce","type":"paragraph","text":"八元八凯之于舜，伊尹之于汤，太公之于文、","index":100,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"a2ee7af3f9","type":"paragraph","text":"武，率五百余年而一遇。生于文、武之后千有余","index":101,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"98db1c50de","type":"paragraph","text":"年，虽孔子之圣，孟柯之贤而不遇，虽太宗之为","index":102,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5eb23bede1","type":"paragraph","text":"君，而未可以必得志于其时也，是亦士民之生于","index":103,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"e7c6f2539c","type":"paragraph","text":"是时者之不幸也。故述其是非得失之迹，非独为","index":104,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"65615fdfe6","type":"paragraph","text":"人君者可以考为，士之有志于道而欲仕于上者，","index":105,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"1936140d73","type":"paragraph","text":"可以鉴奖。[论辨类，曾子固《唐论》]","index":106,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"115608fc4f","type":"paragraph","text":"认识论","index":107,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"28e3e85acf","type":"paragraph","text":"天下有大知，有小知；人之智虑有所及，有","index":108,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c434416872","type":"paragraph","text":"言物可认所不及。圣人以其大知而兼其小知之功，贤人以识，但不能全知其所及而济其所不及。总者不知大知，而以其所","index":109,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"71506ec873","type":"paragraph","text":"不及表其所及。故圣人之治天下也以常，而贤人","index":110,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"89ef27ecdf","type":"paragraph","text":"之治天下也以时，既不能常，又不能时，悲夫始","index":111,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"3fd2ee15b8","type":"paragraph","text":"战！夫唯大知而后可以常，以其所及济其所不","index":112,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"1d095cbeb0","type":"paragraph","text":"及，而后可以时。常也者，无治而不治者也；时","index":113,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c864c20a91","type":"paragraph","text":"也者，无乱而不治者也。[论辨类，苏明允《明","index":114,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"dae5fd1328","type":"subtitle","text":"论》1","index":115,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"7cedad24e9","type":"paragraph","text":"夫臣能读，不能使君必纳读，非真能读之","index":116,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"18a067f4fd","type":"paragraph","text":"臣。君能纳读，不能使臣必读，非真能纳读之","index":117,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"3e70ffbb9b","type":"paragraph","text":"空话连篇","index":118,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"57189602bf","type":"paragraph","text":"君。欲君必纳乎，向之论备奖；欲臣必读乎，吾","index":119,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5c7654cba3","type":"paragraph","text":"其言之。夫君之大，天也；其尊，神也；其威，","index":120,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"9041cff484","type":"paragraph","text":"雷霆也。人之不能抗天、触神、怀雷霆，亦明","index":121,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"64ac8435c5","type":"paragraph","text":"吴。圣人知其然，故立赏以劝之，传日兴王赏读","index":122,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"f7481f585f","type":"paragraph","text":"臣是也。犹惧其选乘阿读，使一日不得闻其过，","index":123,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"7c36322383","type":"paragraph","text":"故制刑以威之。书日：臣下不正，其刑墨是也。","index":124,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5a92345fe6","type":"paragraph","text":"人之情，非病风表心，未有避赏而就刑者，何苦","index":125,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"2dc15a1f82","type":"paragraph","text":"而不读战！赏与刑不设，则人之情又何苦而抗","index":126,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"55c20c3a18","type":"paragraph","text":"天、触神、性雷建战！自非性忠义，不悦赏，不","index":127,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"3ffc2ff70e","type":"paragraph","text":"晨罪，谁欲以言博死者。人君又安能尽得性忠义","index":128,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"f6e6e8389d","type":"paragraph","text":"者而任之。今有三人，一人勇，一人勇快半，","index":129,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c40170df86","type":"paragraph","text":"一人法。有与之临乎渊谷者，且告之日：能跳而","index":130,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"a57ae19e16","type":"paragraph","text":"看何等渊越此谓之勇，不然为法。被勇者耻法，必跳而越谷。若大河深。其勇快半者与快者，则不能也。又告之日：溪，虽有勇者，跳而越者与千金，不然则否。被勇法半者奔利，如不善水，无由必跳而越意，其法者犹未能也。须更，顾见猛虎跳越。此等皆书暴然向遥，则法者不待告，跳而越之，如康庄生欺人之谈。","index":131,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"47aebb6394","type":"paragraph","text":"奖。然则人艺有男快战？要在以势驱之耳。君之","index":132,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"442e5c2035","type":"paragraph","text":"难犯，犹渊谷之难越也。所谓性忠义，不悦赏，","index":133,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"573e786c90","type":"paragraph","text":"不是罪者，勇者也，故无不读；悦赏者，勇快","index":134,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"53a10687f8","type":"paragraph","text":"半者也，故赏而后读；是罪者，法者也，故刑","index":135,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"24c7992028","type":"paragraph","text":"而后读。先王知勇者不可常得，故以赏为千","index":136,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"6f6ce35122","type":"paragraph","text":"金，以刑为猛虎，使其前有所趋，后有所避，其","index":137,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"057b0e6276","type":"paragraph","text":"势不得不极言规失，此三代所以兴也。末世不","index":138,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b4d3b2e4e4","type":"paragraph","text":"然，迁其赏于不读，迁其刑于读，宜乎臣之尝口","index":139,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"e25c21856c","type":"paragraph","text":"卷舌而乱亡随之也。间或贤君欲闻其过，亦不过","index":140,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"7342f759bf","type":"paragraph","text":"赏之而已。鸣呼！不有猛虎，彼法者肯越渊谷","index":141,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"e93aef1685","type":"paragraph","text":"乎？此无他，墨刑之废耳。三代之后，如霍光课","index":142,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b0609fa241","type":"paragraph","text":"昌邑不读之臣者，不亦鲜战！今之读赏，时或有","index":143,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"eec6cb34ee","type":"paragraph","text":"之：不读之刑，缺然无兵。药增其所有，有其所","index":144,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"0dd43bce30","type":"paragraph","text":"无，则读者直，侯者忠，况忠直者乎！诚如是，","index":145,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"1617d9aa48","type":"paragraph","text":"欲闻说言而不获，吾不信也。[论辨类，苏明允","index":146,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"e840fcf024","type":"paragraph","text":"《读论》下]","index":147,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"7e4b988599","type":"paragraph","text":"且吴起与武一体之人也，皆著书言兵，世称","index":148,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"15634be5ea","type":"paragraph","text":"之日孙吴。然而吴起之言兵也，轻法制，草略无","index":149,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5ca64d3725","type":"paragraph","text":"所统纪，不若武之书，辞约而意尽，天下之兵说","index":150,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"57e0fc5707","type":"paragraph","text":"书不足信，皆归其中。然吴起始用于鲁，破齐，及入魏，又","index":151,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c350890029","type":"paragraph","text":"能制秦兵，入楚，楚复霸；而武之所为反如是，诚然。","index":152,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"0a3cad99eb","type":"paragraph","text":"书之不足信也固奖。今夫外御一录，内治一要，","index":153,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"2e802196c1","type":"paragraph","text":"是贼丈夫亦能，夫艺必有人而教之。及夫御三军","index":154,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"929e1dccad","type":"paragraph","text":"之众，营而自固，或且有乱，然则是三军之众","index":155,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"4ce21efc53","type":"paragraph","text":"感之也。故善将者，视三军之众与视一隶一要无","index":156,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"3cb2164884","type":"paragraph","text":"加篇，故其心常若有余。夫以一人之心，当三军","index":157,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"ba7002c3f2","type":"paragraph","text":"之众，而其中恢恢然犹有余地，此韩信之所以多","index":158,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"00490d0b8d","type":"paragraph","text":"多而益辨也。故夫用兵艺有异术战，能勿视其众","index":159,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"1c8d6e4107","type":"paragraph","text":"而已奖。[论辨类，苏明允《权书》六孙武]","index":160,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"0ed6e4314e","type":"paragraph","text":"六国破灭，非兵不利，战不善，在赔秦。","index":161,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"eb83591c7b","type":"paragraph","text":"路秦而力亏，破灭之道也。或日：六国互丧，率","index":162,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"bea0527289","type":"paragraph","text":"略秦耶？日：不路者以路者丧，盖失强援，不能","index":163,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"48a754e939","type":"paragraph","text":"独完，故日辩在略秦也。秦以攻取之外，小则获","index":164,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"4b020d36a0","type":"paragraph","text":"邑，大则得城。较秦之所得与战胜而得者，其实","index":165,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c6bd3cfd6b","type":"paragraph","text":"百倍；诸侯之所亡与战败而亡者，其实亦百倍。","index":166,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"e04d6adc9b","type":"paragraph","text":"则秦之所大欲，诸侯所大惠，固不在战奖。思殿","index":167,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"ac54bcba15","type":"paragraph","text":"先祖父，暴霜露，新荆棘，以有尺寸之地，子孙","index":168,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"f0ed135c08","type":"paragraph","text":"视之不甚惜，举以与人，如弃草茶。今日割五","index":169,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"41ecd6742f","type":"paragraph","text":"城，明日割十城，然后得一夕安衰，起视四境，","index":170,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"ba65f4b999","type":"paragraph","text":"而秦兵又至奖。然则诸侯之地有限，暴秦之欲无","index":171,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"3c5e6b241a","type":"paragraph","text":"庆。奉之弥繁，侵之愈总，故不战而强弱胜负已","index":172,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5c73a7dc8f","type":"paragraph","text":"判奖。至于颠覆，理固宜然。古人云：以地事","index":173,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"94d7ef567f","type":"paragraph","text":"秦，犹抱薪救火。薪不尽，火不灭。此言得之。","index":174,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"7cbcc55e59","type":"paragraph","text":"齐人未尝略秦，终继五国迁灭，何战？与赢而不","index":175,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"bd14767994","type":"paragraph","text":"助五国也。五国既丧，齐亦不免奖。燕赵之君，","index":176,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"42fe94396e","type":"paragraph","text":"始有远略，能守其土，义不略秦。是故燕虽小国","index":177,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"689ccd3c48","type":"paragraph","text":"而后亡，斯用兵之效也。至丹以荆聊为计，始速","index":178,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"1652df51cb","type":"paragraph","text":"锅篇。赵尝五战于秦，二败而三胜，后秦击赵者","index":179,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"4b056fcea2","type":"paragraph","text":"再，李牧连却之。泊牧以逸课，邯郸为郡。惜其","index":180,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"20f14566bb","type":"paragraph","text":"用武而不终也。且燕赵处秦革灭始尽之际，可谓","index":181,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"85b2b7cb11","type":"paragraph","text":"智力孤危，战败而亡，诚不得已。向使三国各爱","index":182,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c0273ce4bd","type":"paragraph","text":"其地，齐人勿附于秦，刺客不行，良将犹在，则","index":183,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"413895930f","type":"paragraph","text":"凡势强力故胜负之数，存亡之理，当与秦相较，或未易量。之联军，军有成鸣呼！以略秦之地封天下之谋臣；以事秦之心礼功者。","index":184,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"9980004ea0","type":"paragraph","text":"天下之奇才；并力西向，则吾恐秦人食之不得下","index":185,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"150cc7dbfa","type":"paragraph","text":"此论未必然咽也。悲夫！有如此之势，而为秦人积威之所","index":186,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c7340ae918","type":"paragraph","text":"动，日削月割以超于亡，为国者无使为积威之所","index":187,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"6d688fd56e","type":"paragraph","text":"劫战！夫六国与秦皆诸侯，其势弱于秦而犹有可","index":188,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"8aac7ed9b9","type":"paragraph","text":"以不赔而胜之之势，药以天下之大，而从六国破","index":189,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"d0f8474188","type":"paragraph","text":"亡之故事，是又在六国下奖。[论辨类，苏明允","index":190,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"d1e48f0024","type":"paragraph","text":"《权书》八六国]","index":191,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"f37178cefc","type":"paragraph","text":"其始误于隆","index":192,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b7c0fba099","type":"paragraph","text":"诸葛孔明奔荆州而就西蜀，吾知其无能为中对，千里之遥也。且彼未尝见大险也，被以为剑门者，可以不而二分兵力。其亡也。吾尝观蜀之险，其守不可出，其出不可终则关羽、刘继，蔬而自安，犹且不给，而何足以制中原备、诸葛三分兵战？若夫秦汉之故都，沃土千里，洪河大山，真力，安得不败。","index":193,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"20f017d4db","type":"paragraph","text":"可以控天下，又乌事夫不可以措足如剑门者而后","index":194,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"a10f4306e1","type":"paragraph","text":"日险战！今夫富人必居四通五达之都，使其财吊","index":195,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"d24f7ba09b","type":"paragraph","text":"出于天下，然后可以收天下之利。有小丈夫者，","index":196,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"614b67048e","type":"paragraph","text":"得一金读而藏诸家，拒户而守之，鸣呼！是求不","index":197,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5037e4f9ca","type":"paragraph","text":"失也，非求富也。大益至，劫而取之，又篇知其","index":198,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"ebcf97091f","type":"paragraph","text":"果不失也？[论辩类，苏明允《权书》十项籍]","index":199,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"39f3b2ba6d","type":"paragraph","text":"其大者非臣之所当言，欲默而不发，则又和","index":200,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b39b457eff","type":"paragraph","text":"自念遭值隆下英圣特达如此，若有所不尽，非忠","index":201,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"f5123125ab","type":"paragraph","text":"言科举无用臣之义，故味死复言之：昔者以诗赋取士，今座","index":202,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"913f9ff536","type":"paragraph","text":"下以经术用人，名虽不同，然皆以文词进耳。考","index":203,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"38133d24db","type":"paragraph","text":"其所得，多吴楚闽蜀之人。至于京东西、河北、","index":204,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"6aa520b0cb","type":"paragraph","text":"河东、陕西五路，盖自古豪杰之场，其人沈勇","index":205,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5846e42878","type":"paragraph","text":"焊，可任以事，然欲使治声律，读经义，以与吴","index":206,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"0324242d89","type":"paragraph","text":"楚闽蜀之人，争得失于毫厘之间，则被有不仕而","index":207,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"002f318107","type":"paragraph","text":"已，故其得人常少。夫惟忠孝礼义之士，虽不得","index":208,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"adfb8410b4","type":"paragraph","text":"志，不失为君子。若德不足而才有余者，因于无","index":209,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"174642ce2d","type":"paragraph","text":"门，则无所不至奖。故臣愿下特为五路之士，","index":210,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"f54dea71c3","type":"paragraph","text":"别开任进之门。汉法都县秀民，推择为更，考行","index":211,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"18a6f91d9b","type":"paragraph","text":"蔡廉，以次迁补，或至二千石，入为公脚。古者","index":212,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"514b034005","type":"paragraph","text":"不专以文词取人，故得士为多。黄霸起于辛史，","index":213,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"816ac25815","type":"paragraph","text":"薛宣奋于书佐，朱邑选于盖夫，邵吉出于狱更，","index":214,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"c98a7f50d3","type":"paragraph","text":"其余名臣循更，由此而进者不可胜数。唐自中叶","index":215,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"5b2986537d","type":"paragraph","text":"以后，方镇皆选列校以掌牙兵，是时四方豪杰，","index":216,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"52e3075236","type":"paragraph","text":"不能以科举自达者，皆争为之。往往积功以取旋","index":217,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"6ec982054c","type":"paragraph","text":"钱，虽老好巨益，或出其中，而名聊贤将，如高","index":218,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"f0f3914de4","type":"paragraph","text":"仙芝、封常清、李光、来填、李抱玉、段秀实","index":219,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"d8cabe3e27","type":"paragraph","text":"之流，所得亦已多奖。王者之用人如江河，江河","index":220,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"34431879b4","type":"paragraph","text":"所超，百川赴搞。蚊龙生之，及其去而之他，则","index":221,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"6ee3bf7635","type":"paragraph","text":"鱼整无所还其体，而献为之制。今世借史牙","index":222,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"159af301d8","type":"paragraph","text":"校，皆奴仆唐人者，无他，以下不用也。今欲","index":223,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"1023933c90","type":"paragraph","text":"用骨史牙校，而骨史行文书，治刑获钱谷，其势","index":224,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"3a28e09eb0","type":"paragraph","text":"不可废鞭糙。鞭糙一行，则豪杰不出于其间；故","index":225,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"3a0c879f0c","type":"paragraph","text":"凡士之刑者不可用，用者不可刑。故臣愿下采","index":226,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"e411e42b7e","type":"paragraph","text":"唐之旧，使五路监司郡守，共选士人以补牙职，","index":227,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"14b32b0d30","type":"paragraph","text":"皆取人材心力有足过人，而不能从事于科举者。","index":228,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"a9b439efe3","type":"paragraph","text":"禄之以今之钱，而课之镇税场务督捕益贼之","index":229,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b806b25cba","type":"paragraph","text":"类，自公罪杖以下听姨。依将校法，使长更得荐","index":230,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"083eba5ff9","type":"paragraph","text":"其才者，第其功阀，书其岁月，使得出任比任","index":231,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"cd7c8b781a","type":"paragraph","text":"子，而不以流外限。其所至，朝廷察其尤异者播","index":232,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"2dd693e926","type":"paragraph","text":"用数人，则豪杰英伟之士，渐出于此涂，而好猜","index":233,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"133235affc","type":"paragraph","text":"之党，可得而笼取也。[奏议类，苏子《徐州","index":234,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"b8d21e705c","type":"paragraph","text":"上皇帝书》]","index":235,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"f33bba10ab","type":"paragraph","text":"自古贤者少，不肖者多。自省事已来，又见","index":236,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"eb1f985c5e","type":"paragraph","text":"就劳动者言，自古贤者贤者恒不遇，不贤者比肩青紫。贤者恒无以自","index":237,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"},{"id":"ab1305cb60","type":"paragraph","text":"存，不贤者志满气得。贤者虽得卑位，则旋而多，不肖者少。死。不贤者或至眉寿。不知造物者意竟如何！无乃所好恶与人异心战！又不知无乃都不省记，任其死生寿天邪？未可知也。「书说类，韩退之《与崔群书》]","index":238,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5"}],"page":{"id":"ca4f227a42","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4e05c334d5","start":278,"end":292}}}},"__N_SSG":true}